WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
Hail Jesus and Mary, dear subscribers of the YouTube channel of the Association "Croatia for Life".

00:00:05.185 --> 00:00:13.702
In our video series, you can watch videos that show what we do, that is, the activities of our Association.

00:00:13.702 --> 00:00:20.474
In this video, you will meet a young, talented and capable lady, and that is our Petra Milković.

00:00:20.474 --> 00:00:27.196
Petra is an excellent organizer of various events of the "40 Days for Life" initiative,

00:00:27.196 --> 00:00:30.735
as she is its director for the whole of Croatia as well as

00:00:30.735 --> 00:00:33.696
the vice-president of the Association "Croatia for Life".

00:00:33.696 --> 00:00:35.507
We meet Petra.

00:00:44.739 --> 00:00:48.016
Hail Jesus and Mary, dear friends, my name is Petra Milković

00:00:48.016 --> 00:00:51.832
and I am the president of the "40 Days for Life – Croatia" initiative.

00:00:51.832 --> 00:00:55.741
Prayer and fasting, peaceful vigil and community outreach

00:00:55.741 --> 00:01:01.595
are the three fundamental pillars of this initiative, on which it has rested for a dozen or more years

00:01:01.595 --> 00:01:05.510
and on which it has been growing all this time and spreading throughout the world.

00:01:06.120 --> 00:01:10.435
How was this initiative actually founded and how did it start?

00:01:10.435 --> 00:01:15.794
In 2004, in a small town of College Station

00:01:15.794 --> 00:01:19.369
in the state of Texas in the United States of America,

00:01:19.369 --> 00:01:22.974
four friends, longtime colleagues in the fight for life,

00:01:22.974 --> 00:01:29.643
concluded that their outcries, their protests, their petitions were not achieving anything

00:01:29.643 --> 00:01:34.535
in order for the newly opened abortion clinic in their city to be closed.

00:01:34.670 --> 00:01:39.266
At that moment, they decided to sit around a small wooden table

00:01:39.266 --> 00:01:47.116
and began to pray for the Lord to tell them what and how to do next.

00:01:47.116 --> 00:01:51.322
So, in prayer, all four received the number 40,

00:01:51.322 --> 00:01:55.577
and we all know that the number 40 is mentioned many times in the Holy Scripture,

00:01:55.577 --> 00:01:59.872
in many different places and in many different events throughout the life of Jesus,

00:01:59.872 --> 00:02:03.768
both in the Old Testament and in the New Testament through many parables.

00:02:03.768 --> 00:02:10.540
They took that number 40 as a frame and decided to keep vigil 24 hours a day in front of their abortion clinic

00:02:10.540 --> 00:02:16.460
and pray for that clinic to be closed and for intentional abortions to stop forever in that clinic,

00:02:16.460 --> 00:02:20.478
in that small town of theirs.

00:02:20.478 --> 00:02:27.817
Already after the first campaign, they managed to reduce abortions by as much as 28%, according to the statistics and the data they had,

00:02:27.817 --> 00:02:35.540
and frankly, after that first campaign, they were worn out, exhausted, they really had no more strength.

00:02:35.540 --> 00:02:40.442
However, the news about them, about how they started such a big thing,

00:02:40.442 --> 00:02:46.920
spread throughout the United States of America, and city by city, little by little,

00:02:46.920 --> 00:02:54.141
people came to them wanting to start something like that in their city and that they would like to have the initiative in their city.

00:02:54.141 --> 00:02:58.435
At that time, it was those four friends, and among them were David Bereit and Shawn Carney,

00:02:58.435 --> 00:03:01.382
 who were the founders of the initiative

00:03:01.382 --> 00:03:07.294
and actually laid the foundations of the initiative, who decided that the initiative would be based on prayer and fasting,

00:03:07.294 --> 00:03:10.456
a peaceful vigil and community outreach,

00:03:10.456 --> 00:03:15.835
and decided that the initiative would hold a peaceful vigil for 40 days twice each year.

00:03:15.835 --> 00:03:19.491
Soon, it just started to spread further and further.

00:03:29.883 --> 00:03:34.781
Before I tell you how this initiative came to Croatia and how it spread throughout our homeland,

00:03:34.781 --> 00:03:37.774
I will refer to the foundations of the initiative, to the three main pillars,

00:03:37.774 --> 00:03:41.877
namely: prayer and fasting, peaceful vigil and community outreach.

00:03:41.877 --> 00:03:46.781
The first pillar of the initiative – prayer and fasting – was not without reason taken as the foundation of the initiative.

00:03:46.781 --> 00:03:53.317
Namely, we dedicate all our prayers and fasts through all 365 days of the year precisely to the intentions of the initiative,

00:03:53.317 --> 00:03:58.081
so that intentional abortion in our homeland and in the whole world will stop forever.

00:03:58.081 --> 00:04:00.371
Prayer and fasting have their foundation in the Holy Scripture

00:04:00.371 --> 00:04:07.848
because Jesus once told us that this kind, this generation, can only be expelled through prayer and fasting.

00:04:08.101 --> 00:04:10.557
The second pillar of the initiative is a peaceful vigil.

00:04:10.557 --> 00:04:16.358
Twice a year for 40 days, we go out in front of hospitals and health centers, in front of abortion clinics,

00:04:16.358 --> 00:04:20.979
not only in our homeland, but also around the world, to pray and keep vigil

00:04:20.979 --> 00:04:24.789
as a last sign of hope for those mothers and fathers

00:04:24.789 --> 00:04:29.082
who think they have no other choice but intentional abortion,

00:04:29.082 --> 00:04:33.945
but as the first sign of love and mercy to those mothers, those fathers and all those 

00:04:33.945 --> 00:04:36.467
who bear the heavy wound of abortion.

00:04:37.111 --> 00:04:44.177
Holding a peaceful vigil is associated with spring and autumn, that’s why they are called spring and autumn campaigns.

00:04:44.177 --> 00:04:48.026
In spring, it always starts on Ash Wednesday and ends on Palm Sunday,

00:04:48.026 --> 00:04:53.594
and the autumn campaign starts at the end of September and always ends at the beginning of November.

00:04:54.284 --> 00:04:58.725
We are often asked why we are right in front of hospitals, health centers and abortion clinics.

00:04:58.725 --> 00:05:03.897
Why are we not in front of the government, the city authorities, the courts, in front of the parliaments?

00:05:03.897 --> 00:05:08.578
However, it is in hospitals, in health centers, in abortion clinics

00:05:08.578 --> 00:05:11.414
that our unborn brothers and sisters lose their lives.

00:05:11.414 --> 00:05:18.629
And that is why we are there to be a sign of hope and a sign of love for all mothers, for all fathers, for all medical staff,

00:05:18.629 --> 00:05:25.732
for all those who carry the wound of abortion, for all those who need hope, to give it to them in that very place,

00:05:25.732 --> 00:05:30.000
where we serve as the last line of defense for that mother and that unborn child.

00:05:30.219 --> 00:05:33.688
And why do we make the local community aware of the problem of abortion?

00:05:33.688 --> 00:05:38.146
No problem in the world right now is bigger than the problem of intentional abortion.

00:05:38.146 --> 00:05:42.195
No crisis, no war, no earthquake, no disease

00:05:42.195 --> 00:05:46.769
takes as many human lives as intentional abortion.

00:05:46.769 --> 00:05:52.476
In particular, more than 50 million human lives are taken every year

00:05:52.476 --> 00:05:58.221
where it should be safest, warmest, most sacred, under a mother's heart.

00:05:58.221 --> 00:06:04.953
50 million of our unborn brothers and sisters annually lose their lives in that way and in that place.

00:06:05.492 --> 00:06:09.880
In 2013, I first heard about the "40 days for life" initiative, and honestly,

00:06:09.880 --> 00:06:14.493
at that time I did not know what it was about or how this initiative was implemented.

00:06:14.493 --> 00:06:20.814
However, the girl who gave me the big news about the initiative came with a sentence:

00:06:20.814 --> 00:06:25.371
Do you know that we have closed two abortion clinics in London?

00:06:25.371 --> 00:06:30.702
I was a little confused then. I looked at her, I didn’t know what exactly it was about.

00:06:30.702 --> 00:06:35.666
And then she explained to me that they had been praying and keeping vigil constantly for several years

00:06:35.666 --> 00:06:37.990
as part of the "40 days for life" initiative

00:06:37.990 --> 00:06:41.869
and asked if we in Croatia would like to have something like that.

00:06:41.869 --> 00:06:48.186
Although I didn’t know exactly what it was about, I knew at that moment that the Lord had lit that one fire in my heart,

00:06:48.186 --> 00:06:53.208
which I feel even today, after ten years that the initiative has existed in our homeland,

00:06:53.208 --> 00:06:58.623
and because of which I do what I do every day, and because of which I participate in the initiative.

00:07:04.214 --> 00:07:07.706
In the meantime, Ante Čaljkušić, the co-initiator of the initiative in Croatia,

00:07:07.706 --> 00:07:13.980
heard about this initiative and our mutual friend brought us together to talk and see

00:07:13.980 --> 00:07:16.900
if we could start something like that in Croatia.

00:07:16.900 --> 00:07:24.091
I didn’t know who Ante was, and today here is one of my closest collaborators, one of my closest friends, and then,

00:07:24.091 --> 00:07:30.135
regardless of the fact that we didn’t know each other, we decided – yes, that’s it, that’s something we want to have in our homeland.

00:07:30.135 --> 00:07:33.232
However, when we launched the initiative, I will be honest,

00:07:33.232 --> 00:07:39.096
we did not expect that it would be launched at such a high speed in many cities in Croatia.

00:07:39.096 --> 00:07:46.031
In Lent 2014, we started the prayer vigil in front of the Clinical Hospital Center of the Sisters of Mercy in Zagreb.

00:07:46.031 --> 00:07:50.696
Hospital by hospital, city by city and this pending campaign,

00:07:50.696 --> 00:07:54.750
as well as every other, more and more cities join.

00:07:54.750 --> 00:08:01.221
This upcoming campaign will involve as many as 38 cities throughout our homeland.

00:08:01.221 --> 00:08:07.265
In fact, all parts of Croatia are involved in some way in this struggle, in this pro-life initiative.

00:08:07.888 --> 00:08:10.749
And why exactly the "40 days for life" initiative?

00:08:10.749 --> 00:08:17.597
It is effective, it is peaceful, it really has fruits and great results.

00:08:17.597 --> 00:08:24.698
More than 160 children were saved because someone kept vigil and prayed in front of Croatian hospitals and health centers.

00:08:24.698 --> 00:08:33.259
Those 160 children are part of more than 23,000 worldwide who have been saved so far precisely because of the initiative.

00:08:33.259 --> 00:08:39.203
We often say that these are only the children we know about and only those children whose testimonies we have heard,

00:08:39.203 --> 00:08:42.166
the testimonies of their mothers whom we have met.

00:08:42.166 --> 00:08:46.551
However, we believe that there are many, many more children

00:08:46.551 --> 00:08:51.395
and even more lives saved that we may not know about and will only find out about in eternity.

00:08:51.395 --> 00:08:55.515
There are also a lot of immediate fruits, friendships, marriages,

00:08:55.515 --> 00:09:00.531
some other little things that we follow and watch and witness every day.

00:09:00.531 --> 00:09:05.391
Miracles are possible and we witness them precisely through this initiative.

00:09:05.391 --> 00:09:09.812
What is very important to us is the salvation of every human soul.

00:09:09.812 --> 00:09:14.960
This is what we know that is also pleasing to God, that our soul is priceless to God

00:09:14.960 --> 00:09:17.667
and that we must fight for every soul.

00:09:17.667 --> 00:09:24.609
We believe that by many prayers, by many fasts that are presented to the Lord with these intentions in mind,

00:09:24.609 --> 00:09:29.405
the human heart can be changed, and we see and witness this through this initiative.

00:09:35.584 --> 00:09:41.421
Finally, I would like to testify to you why it is important to stand right in front of hospitals and health centers,

00:09:41.421 --> 00:09:45.860
why it is important to participate in campaigns and peaceful vigils of the initiative.

00:09:45.860 --> 00:09:49.834
I will tell you the story of two boys who are alive today precisely because of the people

00:09:49.834 --> 00:09:55.808
who stood in front of hospitals and health centers in the snow, ice, storm, wind and sun.

00:09:55.808 --> 00:10:01.898
The first story is about a boy, David, whose mother has already come to the hospital for her scheduled abortion appointment.

00:10:01.898 --> 00:10:07.147
She went inside, she was already at the door, and someone spoke to her in the hallway and said:

00:10:07.147 --> 00:10:10.559
Well, wait a minute, are you sure about your decision?

00:10:10.559 --> 00:10:17.261
She was really distraught, she didn’t want to have an abortion, but she thought she didn’t really have any other choice.

00:10:17.261 --> 00:10:22.677
She didn’t have a job, she already had a little girl, her husband didn’t work either,

00:10:22.677 --> 00:10:24.513
and she thought that an abortion was her solution.

00:10:24.513 --> 00:10:27.097
However, the person who spoke to her said:

00:10:27.097 --> 00:10:33.232
Well, you know, there in front of the hospital someone is praying, and waiting, and keeping vigil, and maybe they can help you.

00:10:33.232 --> 00:10:41.399
Ivana testifies that she went outside, sat down on the sidewalk and literally pulled her hair out because she was completely afraid

00:10:41.399 --> 00:10:45.623
and did not know what her next step was and what to do next.

00:10:45.623 --> 00:10:50.950
However, she took heart, she turned to a single lady who was keeping vigil in front of the hospital at the time,

00:10:50.950 --> 00:10:58.399
and today little David is alive and well precisely because that lady was at the vigil.

00:10:58.517 --> 00:11:02.094
Another testimony that particularly pleases me is the testimony of little Juraj.

00:11:02.094 --> 00:11:07.815
Namely, his mother saw even the volunteers two years before Juraj was conceived.

00:11:07.815 --> 00:11:12.779
You really never know whose life you will change by being there in front of the hospital,

00:11:12.779 --> 00:11:19.001
being there in a place where you may be insulted, where you may be listening to mockery, where you may not be so comfortable.

00:11:19.001 --> 00:11:25.677
However, the mother of our little Juraj passed by the hospital one day to go for some tests.

00:11:25.677 --> 00:11:29.337
And we really got on her nerves, as she tends to say it often.

00:11:29.337 --> 00:11:33.396
She even sent us messages complaining why we were there, what we were doing there.

00:11:33.396 --> 00:11:38.033
We then replied to her messages and she simply forgot about us,

00:11:38.033 --> 00:11:42.304
she waved her hand at everything we argued, everything we told her.

00:11:42.304 --> 00:11:44.978
However, after two years when she became pregnant,

00:11:44.978 --> 00:11:50.762
with a family that did not want to help her, that did not want to support her,

00:11:50.762 --> 00:11:56.113
 with the father of the child who said that he would stand by her with any decision she made,

00:11:56.113 --> 00:12:00.364
and with an already scheduled abortion a day later,

00:12:00.364 --> 00:12:04.965
she remembered that two years ago she saw people praying and keeping vigil in front of the hospital.

00:12:04.965 --> 00:12:09.292
She decided to send us a message again and see what else we can offer her

00:12:09.292 --> 00:12:13.617
as some kind of last branch of hope that she can hold on to.

00:12:13.617 --> 00:12:18.756
That same day we arranged to meet. She met our Dijana, who leads the Team for pregnant women "You are not alone,"

00:12:18.756 --> 00:12:26.118
and today little Juraj is alive and healthy at three years old, and his mother and father are overjoyed to have him in their lives.

00:12:26.303 --> 00:12:33.532
These were just two of the many magnificent stories that were written by God’s hand through this very initiative.

00:12:33.532 --> 00:12:41.655
And that’s why I’m inviting you to get involved as a praying volunteer, like anyone else, to pray and fast for intentions of the initiative:

00:12:41.655 --> 00:12:44.397
for intentional abortion to end forever.

00:12:44.397 --> 00:12:49.997
That this white plague, as blessed Alojzije Stepinac called it, would end forever in our homeland.

00:12:50.132 --> 00:12:56.531
I believe that precisely through the initiative, through prayer and fasting, peaceful vigil and community outreach,

00:12:56.531 --> 00:13:00.844
we will see the beginning of the end of abortion in our homeland and in the world.

00:13:29.456 --> 00:13:33.379
In this video, you met our Petra Milković.

00:13:33.379 --> 00:13:40.287
You can see how much she does in our Association "Croatia for Life", and how big and comprehensive it is.

00:13:40.287 --> 00:13:47.372
All this would not be possible without our praying volunteers, without benefactors

00:13:47.372 --> 00:13:51.568
and without all those who help a child to be born.

00:13:51.568 --> 00:13:55.872
If you want to get involved, feel free to do so –

00:13:55.872 --> 00:14:03.255
pray, fast, donate, contact us, the contacts are in the description of this video. Thank you!

